snippet.title: Paradise Lost Arcade Shooting Game The Island Level
snippet.description: Bronwyn Play's "The Island Level" of the arcade shooter Paradise Lost. I don't think she uses a single grenade! Also the sight was slightly out, so she did go through a lot of credits in her first game of it.
